reviewText: Possibly the best pro wrestling league of all time. Gagne vs. Bockwinkel, Gagne vs. Raschke, High Flyers vs. Ventura&Adonis, Hennigs vs. Road warriors, Lawler vs. Von Erich, Rockers vs. Prettyboys(blllloooooooodeee match; one of the bloodiest EVER!) in an early Sean Micheals match and MORE. Hogan vs. Bockwinkel. 'Nuff said.
